  <summary date="2022-11-09T17:53:28Z" status="Introduced in House">Investigating Russian Ambitions in Nuclear Negotiations Act or the IRAN Negotiations Act

This bill requires the President to, within five calendar days of reaching an agreement with Iran regarding Iran's nuclear program, report to Congress describing any benefits that will accrue to Russia as a result of the agreement.</summary>
